  "title": "日常漫步 Vol.21 之珠海蓝",
  "summary": "蓝色和绿色是绝配的颜色，是大自然的馈赠，是晴空泼洒在水面的倒影，是远山晕染在云海的轮廓。它是自然写给人间的诗，把宁静的蓝、蓬勃的绿，酿成了眼底最治愈的风景。",
  "content": "<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025121712281691.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025121712281780.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1126\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025121712282293.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1126\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025121712282297.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1093\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/20251217122824100.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025121712282586.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\"></p>\n\n<img width=\"1125\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025121712281854.webp\" alt=\"\">\n<img width=\"1125\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025121712282351.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<img width=\"1125\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025121712282341.webp\" alt=\"\">\n<img width=\"1125\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://yayu.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025121712282498.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n<p>蓝色和绿色是绝配的颜色，是大自然的馈赠，是晴空泼洒在水面的倒影，是远山晕染在云海的轮廓。它是自然写给人间的诗，把宁静的蓝、蓬勃的绿，酿成了眼底最治愈的风景。</p>\n<p>图3、图4隔着玻璃拍的，有点变异的蓝。</p>\n<p>By iPhone 12 Pro Max</p>",
